snippet.title: Kinetica - Gameplay Video | PS2 on PS4
snippet.description:
Gameplay footage from Kinetica™ PS2™ game on the PS4™ system. Experience Kinetica™ with 1080p up-rendering and Trophies. Additional enhanced features include Shareplay (Active PS Plus membership may be required), Remote Play, Activity Feeds and Second Screen support for game manuals through the PS Vita system or PlayStation App.

© 2001 Sony Interactive Entertainment America LLC. Kinetica is a trademark of Sony Interactive Entertainment America LLC.

PS2 Classics and PS2-formatted discs are incompatible with the PS4 system.
